
Simplified instructions:

    1. Ensure you have the following software packages installed:

        fuse-devel
        libcurl-devel
        libexpat-devel
        libopenssl-devel
        pkg-config
        zlib-devel

    2. ./configure && make && sudo make install

Please see

    http://code.google.com/p/s3backer/wiki/BuildAndInstall

for more build and install information.

